title: Grilled Eggplant Parmesan
description: If you are a fan of Eggplant Parmesan, then you have to try Sam the Cooking Guy's superb grilled version. It is absolutely scrumptious.

asset.author: Bed Bath & Beyond
asset.hookText:
http://blog.bedbathandbeyond.com/2014/07/grilled-eggplant-parmesan
If you are a fan of Eggplant Parmesan, then you have to try Sam the Cooking Guy's superb grilled version. It is absolutely scrumptious.

transcripts: [MUSIC PLAYING] Eggplant Parmesan is wonderful, but an Eggplant Parmesan sandwich off the grill is a thing of beauty and deliciousness. Start by slicing an eggplant and a large tomato in thick slices. Brush both with olive oil, season with salt and pepper, then put the eggplant on a medium hot grill. While it cooks, combine mayonnaise, minced garlic, and finally chopped basil. Mix well and set aside. Grill the eggplant until it's well marked. Then flip over and top with sliced mozzarella. Then add the tomato slices to the grill. Along with a sliced, crispy bun. When the tomatoes are cooked on both sides, and the buns are browned, build the sandwich. Bun, the garlic basil mayo, eggplant with cheese, tomatoes, and the top bun. Steaks, burgers, and dogs on the grill are great, but this?...Please.
